column3: “Fully relaxing and very long-lasting, the indica-dominance makes for a classically super heavy :) , sometimes i cant move ,it feels like my leg need wheelchairs motherfcker woohoo. :)”

“Took one hit of the hash bowl of this strain and lost all my cool the second it hit the back of my throat.. that's only 5 seconds that u feel like ur gunna melt.. 10 seconds into the high and all u wanna do is lay down and eat”
“One of the best strains I've toked next to Gorilla Glue. Definitely a couch locker off one bowl too the head but too much will leave you useless lol”
“Its the PARANOIED WEED I'll ever tried  pls add this fact into negative aspect of this strain”
